law.history: Repealed 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 132, sec. 32, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 81, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 65, effective July 15, 1998. -- Created 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 443, sec. 65, effective July 13, 1990.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Educational program concerning HIV and AIDS for law enforcement officers.
metadata.lrc-note: (6/20/2005). Under KRS 446.260, the repeal of this section in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 132 prevails over its amendment in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99.
